Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Support AI Engineer position with Nutanix. I bring over three years of professional experience in AI-assisted automation, workflow optimization, and internal tooling, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

